folder: Greenpoint Avenue & Hunters Point Avenue, Queens, NY
original_title: Queens: Greenpoint Avenue - Hunters Point Avenue
text:
Greenpoint Avenue, south side, at Hunters Point Avenue, showing St. Raphaels Roman Catholic Church, the view being
east from near Borden Avenue.
View 1: November 1, 1936
View 2: July 25, 1938
P. L. Sperr
